\begin_inset Formula $s_{a}$
\end_inset

 be the sum of the digits of 
\begin_inset Formula $a$
\end_inset

 in base 
\begin_inset Formula $p$
\end_inset

 and let 
\begin_inset Formula $\mu_{a}=\frac{a-s_{a}}{p-1}$
\end_inset

